parent1.code: A photograph of a black panther prowling menacingly in the style of classic film noir. It slinks stealthily on the gritty, decaying rooftops in the sprawling urban jungle on a chilly night, its piercing emerald eyes gleaming with predatory intent, with flickering streetlamps casting long shadows and thick fog rolling ominously in.

offspring.code: A photograph of a black panther prowling menacingly in the style of classic film noir. It slinks stealthily on the crumbling, rain-slicked rooftops in the sprawling, neon-lit urban jungle on a chilly, moonless night, its piercing emerald eyes gleaming with predatory intent, with flickering streetlamps casting long shadows and thick fog rolling in from the harbor.
